2011-03-31  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	* [fix] Fixing documentation. Adding examples for expressions supported   by turbulence expressions.

	* [fix] Finished work required to support "or" expressions defined.   by coma. Added regression test to check support added.
	* [new] Updated mod-sasl module to allow mod-sasl-mysql extension to check
	  for ip-filter declaration allowing to filter Auth logins attempts using
	  an ip expression. Nice!!

	libvortex-1.1: * [new] Updated vortex connection API to include a new function to return   actual remote peer IP. Unlike vortex_connection_get_host which returns the   connecting name (that may be not an IP) this new function ensures returning   an IP. Updated PyVortex to also support this addition:
	   - vortex_connection_get_host_ip
	   - vortex.Connection.host_ip

	libvortex-1.1: * [fix] Updated documentation to explain on connection accepted   and connection state post created are called twice during TLS   activation.

	* [fix] Adding initial code to support coma separated regexp list. Added   initial regression test. Still more work required.

