	* [fix] Fixed missing file references at mod-sasl.

	* [fix] Updated mod-sasl documentation to explain how to use new   mod-sasl-mysql module. Added extension.modules file example and   included into the installer. * [new] Added a simple tool (gen-mod-sasl-pass.py) to mod-sasl code   to allow creating passwords using the format expected by the module   and as example of code to allow other apps to produce these passwords.

