	* [fix] Added initial changes to make turbulence to be compilable   on windows. More work required.

	libvortex: * [fix] Making vortex channel on created notification to acquire a   reference to the channel during the notificaiton to avoid losing   the reference.

	libvortex: * [fix] Making vortex_channtl_notify_start to return a boolean value   reporting if the notification was done (no matter the value notified).

2007-11-29  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libvortex: * [new] Updated vortex channel API to allow configuring a handler which   is called once the reference is going to be removed from the connection.   This allows to detect channels not closed because the connection have   failed. API added:
	   - VortexOnClosedChannel (handler)
	   - vortex_channel_set_closed_handler

	libaxl: * [fix] fixed documentation (wrong placed).

	libvortex: * [fix] Making vortex_channel_notify_start to not require providing the serverName   value. It is internally stored by the channel until it is used for the notification.

2007-11-28  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libvortex: * [new] Added a new function to the vortex connection module that allows   to get a reference to the listener connection that accepted a particular   connection instance. API added:
	   - vortex_connection_get_listener

2007-11-28  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libvortex: * [fix] Applied Benit Amiaux patch to make realloc functions to call   to axl defined implementation.
	* [new] Updated vortex library start channel notification to allow decoupling
	  the notification from the the reply. Now the application will be able to
	  call vortex_channel_defer_start to signal vortex engine to not reply at
	  this moment. Later, a call to vortex_channel_notify_start confirms if
	  the channel is accepted to be created. API added:

	    - vortex_channel_notify_start_internal
	    - vortex_channel_notify_start

2007-11-28  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libaxl: * [new] Commiting changes proposed by Benoit Amiaux to make axl_new   and the realloc functions to be internally implemented as a function   call openining the posibility to provide application defined   allocation functions. API added:
	   - axl_calloc
	   - axl_realloc

2007-11-26  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	af-arch: * [fix] General update to the turbulence web (fixing typo error   and validation warnings from the w3c validator) and added references   to the turbulence 0.3.0 release (including vortex).

2007-11-23  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	* [fix] Closing release 0.3.0

	libaxl: * [new] Added initial implementation to --htmlize inside the axl-knife   which allows to prepare a xml document to be displayed as html using   simple css.

	* [fix] Added missing index to the db list documentation.

	* [fix] Updated documentation to include some references to the tbc-dblist-mgr   usage and the new support provided by mod-sasl for virtual hosting   configuration.

	mod-sasl: * [fix] Updated core implementation to allow checking if a serverName   parameter has an auth-db activated. Making tbc-sasl-conf to use this   to check the serverName value received. API added:
	   - common_sasl_serverName_exists

	mod-sasl: * [fix] Updated tbc-sasl-conf tool to allow configuring the serverName   value to be used to properly select the auth backend.
	* [fix] Updated backend loading code to better report when some file is
	  missing.

	libvortex: * [fix] Closing release 1.0.11

