	xml-rpc-gen: * [fix] Fixed wrong code produced to handle boolean parameters at   the client stub connector.

	af-gen: * [fix] More bug fixes at the replace interface and fixed a bug   at the code created for the C layer where a custom service   returning a node is defined.

	af-gen: * [fix] Fixed af-gen bug which was producing glib-dependant code   at the replace interface.

	mod-sasl: * [fix] Updated sasl-radmin.idl to makes changes to the operate_sasl_user   service, extending its function to support user disabling and user   remote administrator support.

	mod-sasl: * [fix] Making the db-list loading of remote administrator list, when   it is found a relative path, to use services from vortex_support   module.

	af-arch: * [fix] General update to autoconf files to finally remove glib   from all products, only remaining af-gen.

	afdal-gtk-sharp: * [new] Updated the cil component to include a new class AfDakGtk.cs   that provides binding services to libafdal-glib.

	libafdal-glib: * [new] Added new functions to initialize the library:
	   - afdal_glib_init
	   - afdal_glib_exit

	libafdal: * [fix] Updated afdal request module which was using G_OS_UNIX   and G_OS_WIN32.

	af-gen: * [fix] More de-glibfixation....

	xml-rpc-gen: * [fix] Fixed lost G_OS_WIN32 inside the tool.

	libafdal: * [new] General update to remove the last depedency with glib:   afdal event source and afdal event process modules. These are   now replaced by a generic and configurable implementation that   allows to perform the same tasks, with default handlers, but   at the same time configurable to keep working with gtk+   applications. Module afdal process added, with API:
	   - afdal_process_launch
	   - afdal_process_launch_no_thread
	   - afdal_process_set
	   - (AfDalProcessLaunchFunc)
	   - (AfDalProcessFunc)

