	libvortex: * [fix] Removed some configure.ac variables used by previous   glib dependency. Updated VERSION file.

	libafdal: * [fix] Initial changes to split the library into a general   component and a particular component that supports glib   environments.

	libafdal-glib: * [new] Committing initial working version for this new component   that isolates all the support required to make afdal to work with   glib and gtk environments.

	libafdal: * [fix] Starting library splitting into the general part and the   particular implementation required to properly use af-arch with   Gtk/Glib platforms. Removed afdal_event_source and   afdal_event_process module. Removed both files from the main   include header.

	libafdal: * [fix] Removed not required includes from the afdal password   module.

