	libafdal-af-kernel: * [fix] Library updates due to changes introduced by the af-gen tool.

	af-gen: * [fix] Fixed bug at the C# client layer which was detecting the   the id:int attribute for custom types not using it.

	libvortex: * [fix] commiting changes to the download section, placing a   direct reference to the source code download.

	af-gen: * [fix] Several updates to make af-gen to produce a (C) and (C#)   layer that properly work with the new change introduced in lower   levels to remove the glib dependency. All changes tested to work   with Incident!.

	afdal-sharp: * [fix] Updated the C# binding to remove all code from DataNode class   that was using gobject services to get attribute values from node   references. Updated AfDalList class to use a more efficient API   provided by the AfDalList (C API) module.

