2007-09-21  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	af-gen: * [fix] General changes to the af-gen tool to remove the gobject   and glib dependency. The gobject dependency is completely disabled.   Now remains glib-2.0. GREAT!.

	libafdal: * [fix] General modifications to remove gobject reference from the   library. GREAT!!!! This update also introduces several changes to   remove glib from the library.

	libafdal: * [fix] Removed comments from the afdal event source module.

