2007-09-20  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libafdal: * [fix] General update to remove the GList type from the afdal session,   adfal-request, afdal-datanode and afdal-types.

	libafdal: * [fix] Updated afdal session, afdal datanode, afdal afkyes and afdal   event source to remove GList presense.

	libafdal: * [fix] Removed all references to g_strsplit and its deallocation function.   Updated the code to use axl_stream_split and axl_stream_freev.

	libafdal: * [fix] Updated afdal afkeys module to remove all references to glib and GList.

	libafdal: * [fix] Updated afdal setof module implemenation to remove all references to GList   and glib.

	libafdal: * [fix] Removed all calls to g_setenv, g_getenv and g_unsetenv, replaced by   vortex_support_setenv, vortex_support_getenv and vortex_support_unsetenv.

	libafdal: * [fix] Removed call to g_strtod, replaced by vortex_support_strtod.

	libafdal: * [fix] Removed simbol g_print, replaced by fprintf.

	libafdal: * [fix] Several modifications the the entire library to remove the following   symbols: FALSE, TRUE, g_new, g_new0 and g_free, to replace then with   false, true, axl_new and axl_free.

	libafdal: * [fix] Removed all references to g_return*, replaced by v_return*.

	libafdal: * [fix] Removed gpointer referenced, replaced by axlPointer.

	libafdal: * [fix] Updated afdal_datalist module to use axl hash code. Removed   references to GTree.

2007-09-19  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libafdal: * [fix] Several updates to remove fundamental types from Glib.

	libafdal: * [fix] General updates to conform the new API provided by coyote,   which now do not depends on GLib. Updated source code to be compilable   with -ansi flag.

