	* [fix] Checked default behaviour to not load a database configuration if
	  found two default ones.

	* [fix] Fixed bug inside turbulence_db_list_add and turbulence_db_list_remove   which was causing to not update the first item on the list.

	* [new] Added initial code to implement a regression test for all   modules and the base library provided by turbulence. This helped   to remove a but at the dblist implementation.

