	libaxl: * [fix] Fixed wrong <!DOCTYPE handling at the header. Added a regression test to check   this bug in future releases.

2007-06-19  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libaxl: * [fix] Fixed another bug inside axl_stream_trim* functions which was causing   to not properly handle the basic case where an empty content string is receive   (a string that is totally trimed). Added regression test to check the bug.

	af-arch: * [fix] Updating modules-version.txt and VERSION files.
