2007-06-19  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libafgs: * [new] Updated afgs database module to include a new abstract service that   allows to check the connection created, allowing the module to perform checks   before executing an SQL command. Using this feature now the afgs layer is able   to resume after a database restart (currently only postgresql).
	* [fix] General update to remove gint, gchar, gboolean and gpointer types replacing
	  them with the default types: int, char, bool and axlPointer.

	* [fix] Fixed several minor memory leaks.

	* [fix] Updated afgs config module internals to use axlHash type rather than GTree.

	* [fix] Updated afgs log module to using fopen API rather than the Glib API.

