	af-arch-sharp: * [fix] Making AfDecimal to be more explicit then throwing an exception   due to an empty string to represent a decimal value.

	af-gen: * [fix] Making the tool to allow using "bind as" instructions inside   relations that do not use the 1..1 type. Previously the bind as statement   was limited to 1..1 relation. Updated source code to support the rest   of relations.

