2007-04-16  Francis Brosnan Blázquez  <francis@aspl.es>

	libaxl: * [fix] Updating web to include the latest change notification.

	libaxl: * [fix] Applied change notification: axl-annotate-01. Replaced all reference   to anotate with annoate. Updated libaxl base library, base ns library   and regression tests.

