	libvortex: * [fix] commiting missing def file and main header update.

	libvortex: * [fix] commiting upadtes to the vortex-regression-client.

	libvortex: * [fix] Included initial support to the poll interface, and reworked race   condition fixed previously on windows which was causing problems on linux.

	libvortex: * [fix] Updated compilation files for windows: removed reference to   vortex semaphore module, added vortex thread. * [fix] Fixed race condition at __vortex_connection_set_not_connected.
