	af-arch: * [fix] General update to the af-arch project to remove all references to   the gthread API provided by glib. Removed all references to GStaticMutex,   g_async_queue_* and g_thread_*. Updated logging code to no longer use   g_log functions.

	libvortex: * [fix] Updated regression test to conform with the new changes introduced. Removed   pkg-config reference to gthread-2.0 module. Removed all gthread initialization   code.

	libvortex: * [fix] replace calls to previous message queue API with the new one provided:   VortexAsyncQueue. Replaced all calls to previous logging facilities, using   new one provided by vortex_log. Ensured all regression test work properly.

	libvortex: * [new] Implemented a replacement for GAsynQueue, with the API required:
	   - VortexAsyncQueue (type)
	   - vortex_async_queue_new
	   - vortex_async_queue_ref
	   - vortex_async_queue_unref
